Diaoduapi
=========

api接口插件
1，包括频道的获取
2，最新版本的api interface
3，直播(需要与流媒体服务器配合)

Need
=======
1, devise && faye 
gem install devise
gem install faye

2, how to use
2.1 install use plugin
2.2 create tables:
ruby script/generate diaoduapi names
rake db:migrate



